description: Alamo City Maui Wowi is proud to serve the most delicious, all natural smoothies and coffees from the islands of Hawaii. A great fit for any type of event, we serve the entire San Antonio area. No event is too big or too small. Alamo City Maui Wowi  delivers unique products and exceptional service to your special events. Our menu will to tempt your taste buds and impress your guests with a captivating and unforgettable catering experience.  Our services are designed and available for weddings, convention and corporate events, executive luncheons, social events, non-profit galas, and unique private parties. Our smoothies consist of various fruits, 100% fat free yogurt, a banana, ice, and a small amount of all natural sugar- a delectable combination creating perfect tasting smoothies. Our coffees are selected from the best coffee growing regions in Hawaii- served hot, iced or blended.
name: Maui Wowi Hawaiian Coffees & Smoothies
